              },
              "free_text": [
                " The yields of the elastic and",
                "inelastic scattering were monitored by the same",
                "reaction at a fixed angles of 20 degree."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By compiler.  To obtain the absolute value, a",
                "calibration measurement was made at 20 degree.  This",
                "has been done by measuring the charge collected in",
                "the Faraday cup and by making a precise chemical",
                "determination of the target mass per cm**2.",
                "The calibration measurements were repeated twice, with",
                "three targets each time. An overall reproducibility of",
                "about 10% which represents final uncertainty on the",
                "calibration was found."
              ]
            }
